The paper deals with face parsing, which is a computer vision task related to image analysis and understanding. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a domain adaptation approach, which involves machine learning techniques and algorithms, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models and neural networks, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with caricatures, which are a form of art, making cs.GR (Graphics) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves image synthesis and editing, which are related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
